b' EVL to be Featured in \xe2\x80\x9cChicago New Media 1973-1992\xe2\x80\x9d Exhibition'
b'Home'
b'Recent News'
b''
b''
b''
b' '
b'Sandin, Kooima, Spiegel, and DeFanti,\xc2\xa0Particle Dreams in Spherical Harmonics\xc2\xa0(VR Installation, 2011)'
b'\xe2\x80\x9cChicago New Media 1973\xe2\x80\x931992\xe2\x80\x9d is a public exhibition, to be held November 1 \xe2\x80\x93 December 15, 2018, that illuminates the largely untold story of Chicago\xe2\x80\x99s computer-based art and design legacy, and provides new historical understanding of the artists and organizations that contributed to digital art and technology in the latter half of the 20th Century. The Electronic Visualization Laboratory (EVL) at the University of Illinois at Chicago (UIC) is prominently featured. The exhibition spans the dates EVL was founded (1973) as a joint effort of the UIC Computer Science (CS) department and the School of Art and Design, through EVL\xe2\x80\x99s introduction of the CAVE\xe2\x84\xa2 automatic virtual environment (1992).'
b'The\xc2\xa0\xe2\x80\x9cChicago New Media 1973\xe2\x80\x931992\xe2\x80\x9d exhibition is part of Terra Foundation\xe2\x80\x99s major citywide celebration of the unique and vital role Chicago plays as America\xe2\x80\x99s crossroads of creativity and commerce. It\xc2\xa0is curated by VGA Gallery, an art organization devoted to video games and new media, and will be held at\xc2\xa0Gallery 400, 400 South Peoria St., Chicago, IL 60607.'
b''
b''
b'Supporting Events'
b'November 1, 2018 | 2 \xe2\x80\x93 4 pm'
b'\xe2\x80\x9cChicago New Media\xe2\x80\x9d will host a Symposium, to include EVL co-founders and professors emeritus Tom DeFanti (CS) and Dan Sandin (Art & Design). Reservations are free, but REQUIRED.'
b'Event Details & RSVP Link'
b'November 1, 2018 | 5 \xe2\x80\x93 8 pm'
b'\xe2\x80\x9cChicago New Media 1973\xe2\x80\x931992\xe2\x80\x9d will host an opening event. Exhibiting artists and guests from near and far plan to attend.'
b'Event Details '
b'November 7, 2018 | 6 \xe2\x80\x93 7:30 pm'
b'\xe2\x80\x9cChicago New Media\xe2\x80\x9d is organizing a \xe2\x80\x9cCAVE2\xe2\x84\xa2 Demonstration with Dan Sandin,\xe2\x80\x9d to be held at EVL. Sandin will demo his experiential artwork \xe2\x80\x9cParticle Dreams in Spherical Harmonics\xe2\x80\x9d in the CAVE2 hybrid-reality environment. Reservations are free, but REQUIRED.'
b'Event Details & RSVP Link'
